A Run contains the sequencing results from a particular run on a sequencing instrument. The Run was done in fulfillment of an Experiment that was designed into the Study. One SRA run may consist of only a portion of the plate or slide if the instrument run was partitioned among distinct experiments or between distinct RUNs. By policy the Center should separate these data into distinct SRA Run objects.
